Content.summary: 'Once again' - a blog post by Darren Ferguson about Human Interest written on 02 July 2006
Content.bodyText:
Ouch.

Well, all I can say is that luck always plays a part. Our Wayne just wasn't quite up to it when the pressure was on.

I have plenty of complaints and a overwhelming feeling of injustice, but I try to be dignified in defeat and won't say any more.

I must be getting old, I am used to this feeling. I'll be back up on my feet and smiling again in 3 or 4 days.
